    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just about how i feel, it's about what i'm doing to them. every time i mess up or struggle, i'm taking energy away from them that should be going toward their future. i'm just a constant drain on everything they have. if i weren't here, they wouldn't have to worry about me or deal with the fallout of my mistakes. they'd finally just be able to breathe.",
