    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so selfish to keep clinging to this life when it's clearly making their lives worse. like, if i actually cared about them, i'd want them to have the best possible chance, and right now i'm the thing standing in the way of that. wouldn't it actually be more selfless to just... step aside and let them be happy without me?",
